de_fortaleza is open for public use however the content which is copyrighted by Valve remains Valve property, all rights reserved.

de_fortaleza was created by Surreal for fun, and is not intended to make profit in any way.

Please feel free to share and play this map, I hope you enjoy.

Some bugs I found after release. Unable to fix at this point since I am short on time. My apologies.

- Small gap in stairs at bombsite B.
- Lower wall in the back is accesible, some roofs can be reached, however the map is still sealed.
- Map requires increased number of spawn entities (6 at this points for both t and ct).
